## 3. 🔧 Setup & Dependencies

### Private Properties (Mock Objects)
Deklarasikan semua dependencies sebagai private properties:

```php
private $prakarsarepo;
private $prakarsamediumrepo;
private $masterservice;
private $eksternalservice;
private $officeservice;
private $coreLasService;
private $masterasuransirepo;
private $kreditInvestasiPadatKaryaUsecase;
private $kreditUsahaAlsintanUsecase;
private $prakarsaHistoryRepo;
```

### Method `setUp()`
Dijalankan sebelum setiap test method:

```php
protected function setUp(): void
{
    parent::setUp();

    // Mock semua dependencies
    $this->prakarsarepo = Mockery::mock(PrakarsaRepository::class);
    $this->prakarsamediumrepo = Mockery::mock(PrakarsaMediumRepository::class);
    $this->masterservice = Mockery::mock(MasterService::class);
    $this->eksternalservice = Mockery::mock(EksternalService::class);
    // ... dan seterusnya
}
```

### Method `tearDown()`
Cleanup setelah setiap test method:

```php
protected function tearDown(): void
{
    \Mockery::close();
    parent::tearDown();
}
```

### Helper Method `makeService()`
Membuat service instance dengan dependencies ter-mock:

```php
protected function makeService()
{
    return Mockery::mock(KreditPembiayaanPerumahanUsecase::class, [
        $this->prakarsarepo,
        $this->prakarsamediumrepo,
        $this->masterservice,
        $this->eksternalservice,
        // ... dependencies lainnya
    ])->makePartial();
}
```

**Penjelasan**:
- `.makePartial()` = method nyata tetap berjalan, hanya dependencies yang di-mock
- Gunakan `.makePartial()` untuk test method behavior dengan mock dependencies

