## 4. 🧪 Penulisan Test Method

### Naming Convention
Format: `test{MethodName}{Scenario}`

```php
// ✅ BAIK
testDoSendAkadAgunanThrowExceptionWhenPrakarsaNotFound()
testDoSendAkadAgunanAgunanNotFound()
testDoSendAkadAgunanFailSendSIKP()
testGetDetailPrakarsaKPPHistoryForProduct68ReturnsExpectedStructure()

// ❌ HINDARI
testSomething()
test1()
testMethod()
```

### Struktur Test Method (AAA Pattern)
```php
public function testDoSendAkadAgunanThrowExceptionWhenPrakarsaNotFound()
{
    // ARRANGE: Setup data & expectations
    $this->expectException(DataNotFoundException::class);
    
    $prakarsa = Mockery::mock(Prakarsa::class);
    $prakarsa->shouldReceive('toArray')->andReturn([]);
    
    $this->prakarsarepo->shouldReceive('getPrakarsa')
        ->once()
        ->andReturn($prakarsa);
    
    // ACT: Jalankan method yang di-test
    $service = $this->makeService();
    $service->doSendAkadAgunan("REF001", "123456");
    
    // ASSERT: Verify results
    // (assertions implisit dari Mockery expectations)
}
```

