## 7. 🔍 Assertions & Verifications

### Basic Assertions
```php
$this->assertTrue($result);              // Assert true
$this->assertFalse($result);            // Assert false
$this->assertNull($result);             // Assert null
$this->assertIsArray($result);          // Assert array
$this->assertIsString($result);         // Assert string
$this->assertIsInt($result);            // Assert integer
$this->assertIsObject($result);         // Assert object
```

### Value Assertions
```php
$this->assertEquals($expected, $actual);           // Assert equal
$this->assertNotEquals($expected, $actual);        // Assert not equal
$this->assertSame($expected, $actual);             // Assert identical (strict)
$this->assertNotSame($expected, $actual);          // Assert not identical

$this->assertGreaterThan(5, 10);                   // Assert greater than
$this->assertLessThan(15, 10);                     // Assert less than
$this->assertGreaterThanOrEqual(10, 10);           // Assert >= 
```

### Collection Assertions
```php
$this->assertCount(3, $array);                     // Assert count
$this->assertEmpty($array);                        // Assert empty
$this->assertNotEmpty($array);                     // Assert not empty
$this->assertContains('value', $array);            // Assert contains
$this->assertNotContains('value', $array);         // Assert not contains
```

### String Assertions
